    "description": "Join the 5paisa International Enterprises family as a Financial Analyst in Dhanbad. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout 5paisa International Enterprises:\n5paisa International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with 5paisa International Enterprises!",
